collections.name: a2p-v1
collections.description:
The a2p project is an artist-led online exchange. It explores new ways of sharing and trading digital artworks: images, videos, and animations.

It’s a speculative exploration into new ways of distributing and sharing digital images, videos, and animations. We’re a group of artists selected by four artist/curators: myself, Rick Silva, Addie Wagenknecht, and exonemo (SEMBO Kensuke and AKAIWA Yae).

Each of us has created a new artwork and has released it as an edition of ten along with one artist proof. We’re across many time zones and continents, but for one week, we’ll occupy a shared online space where we’ll trade work. It’s a performance, but also a way of sharing our work with fellow artists and a way to think about what happens to the work after it’s made. It’s an artist-to-artist system to build and curate a collection of work.

collections.name: The cat with the red mask
Imagine Salaam/Shalom
collections.description:
Imagine Salaam/Shalom (“Peace” in Arabic/Hebrew a ’la Yoko Ono's "Imagine Peace") is a Charity NFT Collection that draws on the unique perspective of the Live Encyclopedia: Large Nature Model. In 500 unique digital pieces, the project hallucinates imagined possibilities when two male soldiers, one Israeli and one Palestinian, are disarmed, stripped of their uniforms, and subsequently transported to a utopian shared space. Removed from their locals of Gaza, Tel Aviv, or Jerusalem, the men become reacquainted in an underwater biblical Garden of Eden falling into the depth of the Mediterranean Sea. Their human, sensual, and intimate lives are revealed and showcased with a generative AI model dedicated to the natural world. As witnesses, we are invited to Imagine Peace and Wage Hope.

Imagine Salaam/Shalom benefits two non-profit organizations: The joint Israeli-Palestinian Parents Circle Families Forum and Doctors Without Borders/Médecins Sans Frontières.

collections.name: Ethereal Elementals: Celestial Guardians.
collections.description: "Ethereal Elementals: Celestial Guardians" is a legendary NFT series that brings to life ancient cosmic protectors born from the forces of the universe. Each Guardian represents a unique elemental power—Solar Lion, Lunar Owl, Nebula Wolf, and more—all designed with stunning celestial details, glowing energy, and rich lore. Collectors can own a piece of this mythical universe, where every Guardian tells a story of balance, power, and timeless beauty. Discover the harmony of celestial fire, cosmic tides, and astral wisdom in a collection that celebrates the boundless creativity of the cosmos.

collections.name: Clouds over the river
collections.description:
Immerse yourself in the tranquil beauty of nature with Clouds Over the River, an original painting that captures the serene moment when a river reflects the soft, drifting clouds above. The gentle hues of blue, gray, and soft whites dance across the canvas, evoking a peaceful, calm atmosphere. The flowing river's surface mirrors the sky's ever-changing colors, while delicate brushstrokes bring texture and depth to the composition. Perfect for anyone seeking a moment of quietude in their space, this piece embodies the harmony between water and sky, nature’s timeless elegance.

Whether displayed in your living room, study, or as a serene focal point in a cozy corner, Clouds Over the River invites the outdoors inside, offering a calming visual escape.

collections.name: thegodfather
collections.description: Immerse yourself in the enigmatic aura of "The Godfather: Authority in Shadows." This NFT captures the essence of power and respect embodied by the iconic figure, Vito, clad in a dark, elegant suit with a striking red tie. Seated in a luxurious leather chair, he holds the reins of control, a lit cigar poised between his fingers, emitting wisps of smoke that blend into the shadows of the dimly lit room. This digital artwork encapsulates the timeless allure of the classic gangster era, rendered in a style that echoes the gritty, moody atmosphere of crime films. Own a piece of this formidable persona, a symbol of authority and influence in the intricate world of organized power.

Aphrodite – Goddess of Love & Desire 💫🌹

Behold Aphrodite, the radiant embodiment of love, beauty, and passion, reimagined in this exclusive NFT. Emerging from the sea foam, she captivates with her ethereal glow, golden aura, and the power to enchant all who gaze upon her. Adorned with roses, pearls, and flowing silk, every detail of this piece symbolizes her divine allure and eternal grace.

This one-of-a-kind NFT is a tribute to the goddess who has inspired lovers, poets, and warriors for centuries. Holders of Aphrodite will unlock exclusive perks, including access to mythology-inspired digital experiences, collector rewards, and future metaverse integrations.

Own the essence of divine beauty.
